* Main changes Changelog

** Release 5.x
Compatibility with the AIML standard files
New aiml_parser.py
Under development

** Release 4.x
AIML-like engine based on JSON files
Windows and Linux distributable package

** Release 3.x
Releases with multiplatform STT /TTS VOICE functions enabled
Windows and Linux distributable package
15 languages available

** Release 2.x
Releases with VOICE functions enabled (STT multiplatform, TTS only for windows)
Italian and English Language
Windows and Linux distributable package
distributed from GitLab, repository mirror only on GitHub

** Release 1.x
First stable releases
Italian Language only
Windows distributable package
distributed from GitHub
